{"tid":620966,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴應該出12小時先一班嘅\"關愛車\"","createTime":"2018-04-08T01:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T06:39:06.000Z","uid":65346,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6dc74f86a99da371f9c9e794ff74a0517d091321","tid":620966,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T01:46:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180408/58046246\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F58046246&d=6sBp%2F%2FOpXbirerEnLVeCCoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=0cedb6ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F58046246&h=47a07981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180408/58046246</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n凌晨近零時，一輛由小西灣開往黃大仙的九巴106號線隧道巴士，在銅鑼灣告士打道景隆街站上落客時，一名肥身材姓林(40歲)男子與妻子、嬰兒及母親上車。<br />\n<br />\n當時巴士並未客滿，下層仍有座位，而車內右方兩個關愛座，靠窗位置坐有一名手抱嬰兒的女士，另一靠走廊座位坐有一名戴眼鏡姓吳(33歲)男子。肥男走前要求他讓座給老人家，但該名操內地口音的男子拒絕，雙方發生爭執。<br />\n據同樣在景隆街站上車的乘客王小姐稱，兩人以粗言互駡，繼而動手扭作一團，歷時約1分鐘，其後被乘客制止，據稱是新移民的鄉音男被打到流鼻血，眼鏡打歪。<br />\n當時九巴駛至告士打道上橋位，車長報警並停車等候，但有乘客趕火車要求車長開車，最後車長開車過紅隧，在康莊道巴士站才停車，等候警察到來。警方接報到場，兩人分別鼻傷及頭痛不適送院，同涉打架被捕。"},{"pid":"a23d63dd2e792ae79f3c3131ffd408bb39e7cc99","tid":620966,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:01:42.000Z","msg":"要求開車既乘客仲惡過打人果位?<br />\n個巴士佬又真係走去開車"},{"pid":"6e204d4b5ab3c248b10d8e32c1195d0d1858706d","tid":620966,"uid":67353,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"趕火車仲走去打boss搭106係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fe85ce059a99290c703fc714c909c6f0f37f24","tid":620966,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:13:23.000Z","msg":"應該要教育下新移民，同埋批佢落來大陸公安喎"},{"pid":"1d29b80191b64735214916b9aca01cf34bdbfb11","tid":620966,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569a1747259a1705c1d1991fdd1ba0300fe38a11","tid":620966,"uid":170159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e204d4b5ab3c248b10d8e32c1195d0d1858706d","tid":620966,"uid":67353,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"趕火車仲走去打boss搭106係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"呢個好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa2e1a1f5c5e17b64c5bdf0cdb6b797bbd0d486","tid":620966,"uid":739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6e204d4b5ab3c248b10d8e32c1195d0d1858706d","tid":620966,"uid":67353,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"趕火車仲走去打boss搭106係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:39:06.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全程 106 就話耐姐<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣去紅磡最快係 106 同 102 , 一個站就到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}